{"tid":982382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭友人脅迫交出提款卡 男子失3萬8千元","createTime":"2019-01-15T05:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T06:04:22.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ce28d7466772c5783b432227002d053bab519204","tid":982382,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547508691_f580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547508691_f580.jpg&h=7d940476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角太子道西90號，凌晨3時許，一名26歲姓陳男子在一間酒店房間內，遭友人及兩名南亞漢威脅，交出銀行提款卡和密碼。3人取走銀行卡後離開，事主尾隨追出及致電報警。警員到場展開調查，事主發現戶口被人提走38,000元，警方暫列勒索案件處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190115/59143659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F59143659&d=a6jwj76mG8mcAc9%2FaZOaek%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2dbf0060\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F59143659&h=7db1a66b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190115/59143659</a>"},{"pid":"ebc409d23a9927b89183c0e3586c5713bc866e08","tid":982382,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"四皮野睇清一個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d363d2af5c3d760921e9f985de1adb19d2bcea46","tid":982382,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce28d7466772c5783b432227002d053bab519204","tid":982382,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547508691_f580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appled